While a Vampire Lord looks like a gargoyleΓÇöhard, winged, statuesque, terrifyingly "clean"ΓÇöthe Vrykolas Lord is soft, wet, and teeming with life.
Appearance: Alfonso grows in mass, not height. His skin splits to reveal a chitinous, insectoid under-layer (Peryite) draped in wet, fungal robes of living flesh (Namira). He does not have bat wings; he has a mantle of writhing feeder-tendrils or insect swarms.
